Recommends: valkey-server (>= 9.1) | valkey (>= 9.1)
Description: LuaJIT scripting engine module for Valkey
 A LuaJIT scripting engine module for Valkey that replaces the built-in
 Lua 5.1 interpreter with LuaJIT v2.1, providing JIT compilation and
 optional FFI support for high-performance scripting.
